29 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 6-16-103 is amended to read as follows:
30 6-16-103. Course of study generally — Online portal required —
31 Definitions.
32 (a) There shall be taught in all of the public or elementary schools
33 of in this state subjects that may be designated by the State Board of
34 Education or as required by law.
35 (b) Nothing in this section shall be construed to prohibit the
36 inclusion of additional subjects in the state course of study or in any
